source.inline: if application "Spotify" is running thentell application "Spotify"if player state is playing thenreturn (get artist of current track) & " – " & (get name of current track)elsereturn ""end ifend tellend ifreturn ""

actionAppleScript.inline: if application "Spotify" is running thentell application "Spotify"if player state is playing thennext trackend ifend tellend if
